  <PawnAttackedInDarknessText>黑暗中有東西攻擊了{0_nameDef}！\n\n除非{0_pronoun}安全回到光線下，否則攻擊會持續下去。</PawnAttackedInDarknessText>
  <!-- EN: Noctol attack -->
  <NoctolAttackLetterLabel>夜行者攻擊</NoctolAttackLetterLabel>
